The '''Headstrong'''s were a [[Hobbits|Hobbit]] family, probably well-to-do,<ref>{{HM|Guide}}, p. 192</ref> although they were not included in Tolkien's list of wealthier Hobbit families.<ref name="L|25">{{L|25}}</ref> The only known member of the family, [[Malva Headstrong]], married [[Gormadoc Brandybuck]], a notable [[Master of Buckland]].<ref>{{App|Brandybuck}}</ref>
